name: Baahubali 2: The Conclusion
review:
A certain classy visual delight and a must watch for Baahubali lovers. Not strong in content, substandard story, few good characters but not able to withstand the expectations and the excitements that the wonderful part 1 created. It has good fight scenes and a decent love story again but the movie hasn't left the required impact.
